# ConnectedAccountView Component

The `ConnectedAccountView` component provides an overview of all financial accounts connected to the platform. It displays a unified view of bank accounts, credit cards, investment accounts, and other financial products linked through APIs. This component enables users to manage their connected accounts, monitor their status, and navigate to detailed views.

