## Usage Example

Here's a basic usage example of the `ConnectedAccountView`:

```tsx
<Canvas>
  <Story name="Default">
    <ConnectedAccountView
      connectedAccounts={[
        {
          id: "inst-1",
          name: "Chase Bank",
          logo: "/logos/chase.png",
          connectionStatus: "connected",
          lastUpdated: "2023-05-15T14:30:00Z",
          accounts: [
            {
              id: "acc-123",
              name: "Business Checking",
              type: "CHECKING",
              balance: 12450.75,
              currency: "USD"
            },
            {
              id: "acc-124",
              name: "Business Savings",
              type: "SAVINGS",
              balance: 45250.00,
              currency: "USD"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          id: "inst-2",
          name: "Capital One",
          logo: "/logos/capital-one.png",
          connectionStatus: "connected",
          lastUpdated: "2023-05-15T16:45:00Z",
          accounts: [
            {
              id: "crd-456",
              name: "Business Visa",
              type: "CREDIT_CARD",
